data.description:
Dont miss out on this one time owner home. This East side charmer is nestled in the coveted Ivy Hill subdivision. This spacious 3-bed, 2-bath home offers 1600+ sq feet of comfortable living. The heart of the house is the large kitchen and dining area that seamlessly connects to the inviting living room, creating the perfect space for gatherings and day-to-day living. Unwind in the master suite, complete with a spacious master bathroom featuring both a shower and a stand-alone bathtub. The flexible layout includes an additional room that can easily be transformed into a den, office, or even a 4th bedroom to suit your unique needs. Step outside to a delightful enclosed patio, providing an extension of your living space, perfect for relaxation or entertaining, all w/ permits. For garden enthusiasts, complete with a mini 6-hole golf course, adding endless entertainment options. You'll also find an abundance of fruit trees, offering a touch of nature's bounty right in your own backyard.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this property your own, where comfort, elegance, and outdoor enjoyment come together harmoniously. Schedule a viewing today to explore the possibilities and envision the lifestyle that awaits you in this remarkable home.
